---
title: Crispy Chicken Milanese with Roasted Butternut Squash and Tomatoes
description: The secret to perfect chicken Milanese is butterflying the meat. Not only does this technique reduce cook time, but it also allows the panko and sour cream breading to coat a larger surface area. Try not to slice all the way through the chicken breast, but if you do, don’t sweat it! We promise it will be just as delicious!
